                    <enclosure url="https://github.com/Bengerthelorf/Claudit/releases/download/v0.0.4/Claudit.dmg"
                    sparkle:edSignature="UhmJosYYqpUIM5sqcLEkz6+rX1orJtNDVDmZntxukWBjRZqAUY5utZqiCFbjCpvzhmm2MPgtkSk69PsIAwz7Ag==" length="4151718"
                    type="application/octet-stream"/>
                    <description>
                        <![CDATA[
                    <h2>Version 0.0.4</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Refactor:</strong> code quality cleanup</li>
                        <li><strong>Refactor:</strong> replace SwiftUI App with pure AppKit entry point</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> prevent phantom window flash on launch</li>
                        <li><strong>Refactor:</strong> Settings with NavigationSplitView, close phantom window</li>
                        <li><strong>Refactor:</strong> replace SwiftUI Settings scene with manual NSWindow</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> observe Settings window appearance before activating</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> Settings window focus on first open after launch</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> use 50ms delay for first-launch window activation</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> launch-at-login status and window focus activation</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> hide future days in calendar heatmap, add unit tests</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> allTimeDailyMap year collision, heatmap hover, consistent heights</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> MonthHeatmap missing days, remove toolbar separator line</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> show time range filter on Activity page, hide toolbar separator</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> hide open-in-window toolbar button when no session is selected</li>
                        <li><strong>Refactor:</strong> use process.terminationHandler instead of blocking waitUntilExit</li>
                        <li><strong>Refactor:</strong> add @MainActor to AppState and AppDelegate</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> guard date formatters with NSLock instead of nonisolated(unsafe)</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> session window observer leak and stale remote cache cleanup</li>
                        <li><strong>Fixed:</strong> replace silent catch blocks with os_log, remove force unwraps</li>
                        <li><strong>Refactor:</strong> extract shared SessionMessageList to deduplicate session views</li>
                        <li><strong>Refactor:</strong> extract shared SSHService to eliminate SSH code duplication</li>
                    </ul>
                        ]]>
                    </description>
                </item>
